INSTALL UNDER UNIX

  You need the ocaml compiler installed. It must be accessible in the path.

  Do:
     ./configure
     make
  Optionnally do:
     make bootstrap    # checks camlp4 by itself
     make opt          # make the native-code library
     make opt.opt      # make other native-code programs
  Become root and do:
     make install

INSTALL UNDER WINDOWS

  Under Windows, you need the Cygwin environment. The above directives
  apply.
